    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and clear coat peeling on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster. While all essential features like the heater and lights work, some secondary controls may feel stiff. It\u2019s a functional choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 21500.0,
