    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits no signs of wear, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies even the most discerning collector. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, the vehicle remains mechanically and aesthetically peerless. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering in its most refined state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
