    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in iconic Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is anchored by a variable M-Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically flawless: the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, rod bearings replaced preventatively, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to eliminate fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A true driver\u2019s machine preserved in its peak performance envelope.",
